cism, sexism, or how ugly someone's kid is, but that's a sligthly different thing.)<br><br>Anyhow, that's my thoughts for now.  <br><br>AlAaraaf.<br>"Death is coming..."<br>&nbsp;<br>"Te aurdire no possum. Musa sapienum fixa est in aura."</td></tr>
