	   <tr><td colspan=2>Lets start right away:<br> When you ask the average person what an adult game is, they say porn. Well there are porn games but adult entertainment should mean entertainment for adults in general.<br>There has recently been an explosion in  adults playing video games because those that grew up with an Nes are now adults. Therefore they are demanding games that suit their tastes. Well thier prayers have been answered. However, in my opinion, adult games look more like teenage games: Big guns, lots of gore and lots of hot girls. Sure resident evil is for adults as well as the MK series but how many accually do play it other than teenagers and college students(while technically adults the adults i am referring to are 25+)? I am sure allot but come-on those are marketed to teenagers and you know it.<br>Adult games should be defined as two fold:<br>1) enough mature themes in order for adults to enjoy it, but not so much that it turns into a teenage game.<br>2.) A level of sophistication that is adult level. Thats not to say mindless games aren't for adults, my father will sometimes play goldeneye with me; but its still a teenage game.<br>Some games that i have played that under my system are adult games.<br>Max Payne: This game is violent and dark fulfilling part one, but it excels in story telling and has heavy themes.<br>Civ III: While it does not have the mature themes, the level of sopistication goes above allot of younger peoples heads.<br>Doac: The wild card, yes teenagers play it but a large population of players are adults, WHY? because of the social aspects and the atnosphere and frankly they just do.<br>Not adult games:<br>MK series: HAHAHAAHAHAH, this nothing but a violent game that apeels and is markets to teenagers. Nuff said.<br>Resident evil: Middle of the road. gory, bloody but it has some sophistication to it.<br><br>  In conclusion, the video game industry has the right idea, but not there yet because adult games are not that different from teenage games.  People are free to play what they want, I am mearly defining what should be called an adult game.<br>Roshi out.<br><br>Discussion for this week.<br>Now I may be off on this subject so feel free to comment on this becuase i can be a little off, so go ahead give critizim(but be nice!!!!!)<br>&nbsp;<br>current Doac Player;<br>Former eq player.</td></tr>
